content=Westfield Brandon Town Center has several things to offer shoppers visiting. From several popular clothing shops such as Express, Abercrombie & Fitch, G by Guess, Hollister, to restaurants such as The Cheesecake Factory, California Pizza Kitchen, and a full foodcourt. There is plenty to see here and plenty of places to entertain kids including an arcade, trampoline jumping, merry go-round, and playground.

content=If you're on a budget, but still want some quality food then Cheddar's is the place for you. For the same price as McDonald's you can have some real burgers. They have steak and seafood options as well for much cheaper and better then you will find in other places. Voted the Best Restaurant in Brandon many times as well.

content=If you're looking for some great Thai food then this is the place in Brandon to go to. From great soups and curries, to tasty noodles such as Pad Thai, and sweet desserts, Ploy Thai has plenty offer Thai food lovers.
content=Nice atmosphere and reasonable prices at this Brandon institution.  The Sheppard's Pie is great, and so is the menu.  Variety of pub foods and drinks.  Okay for families before 8PM.
